			<div class="status">
				<div class="title">Dragon Details</div>
				<div class="param">
					<ul>
						<li>Valyx's pactwyrm commands lightning itself, and<br>has taken the title of Fulminator. Thor possesses<br>power great enough to reduce battlefields to ash,<br>and his beliefs as a warrior also influence the<br>man with whom he has sworn a pact.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div></div><div class="skill explanation">
	<div class="title">Skills</div>
	<dl><dt
				>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/b3eeeb36b0d4aed9820f32abb1dd51022.png"></span>
				<span>Thor's Hammer</span>
			</dt>
			<dd>
				<div>
					Deals light damage to the target and nearby enemies,<br>and inflicts paralysis. Continually tapping the screen<br>while charging the attack will increase damage,<br>with damage reaching its maximum potential at<br>stage three. The attack will be unleashed after a<br>set time or upon reaching stage three.
				</div>
			</dd>
	</dl></div><div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/3a59dbd2051c2865bdfc9245c709a80a2.png"></span><span>(Light) Chariot Rider V</span></dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Light: <br>increases strength by 50%, increases the user's<br>energy level by one stage for every 5 seconds<br>that pass, and provides a further increase to<br>the user's strength based on the user's<br>energy level, up to a maximum of 45%<br>when the user is energized.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/3a59dbd2051c2865bdfc9245c709a80a2.png"></span><span>(Light) Thunder Bringer II</span></dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Light: <br>When the user's shapeshift is undone,<br>energizes the entire team.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>■Regarding Gala Thor&#39;s Attacks</div><div>By continuing to tap the screen during the third attack of Gala Thor&#39;s standard combo, you can continue to attack with the third attack of his standard combo, up to a certain number of times.</div><div><br></div><div>
