			</dt>
			<dd>
				<div>
					Deals shadow damage to the target<br>and nearby enemies, and decreases<br>the remaining time of Locked Sigil<br>by 60 seconds if the attack connects.<br>During Sigil Released, this skill instead<br>deals shadow damage to the target<br>and nearby enemies, and deals bonus<br>damage to enemies in buff zones created<br>by both the user and other adventurers.<br>Bonus damage will be greater against<br>enemies in buff zones created by the user.
